{
  "stem": "15768.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "One night, I remember, we were camped in a ditch actually for the night when a farmer came out and said, now, do come in and spend the night with us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we spent the night with them in the cellar, where there were two mattresses on the floor.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the children were allowed to stretch out on the mattresses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember thinking, you know, how marvelous to be finally laid down on something other than earth and fell asleep, soundly asleep, and did not hear the bombings during the night.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then we continued on the next day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when we finally got to the border-- I really don't remember how many days it took us, probably four, I would think-- we had hoped to, because it was a crowd that was trying to get into France, to kind of go with-- get lost in the crowd and that way be able to get over the French border without too much difficulty.",
      "word_count": 64
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, when we got there, they asked people to hold up their identification papers.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And ours, being of German origin, were white.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the others were blue.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they picked out all the white and pulled us aside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we spent an anxious day waiting on the side while everybody else went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And then they put us on the truck and took us off to a internment camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And initially, that internment camp was really for German prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The women and children were separated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were about 480 women and children, a sizable camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I'm in the process of trying to find out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have not been able to place it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- my father was in a barbed wire area with the German prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
